> Tanks only survive if they get about 4000+HP and at least 250 of each defense

{{champion:14}} Get upwards of 6000 health with {{item:3053}}

Also, this may sound weird, but League of ADCs is the healthiest meta. Assassins have a place in killing the ADC since they are so important. Tanks have a place through soaking damage and providing strong crowd control. Mages have a place through their long range poke for siege and their utility. Supports need to be taken to babysit the ADC. Fighters are a hybrid Tank and Assassin, so they are good for evening out a team's damage in any meta. ADC is good for League of ADC. All roles are needed in League of ADC, although Tank suffers the most since they are countered through sustained damage. Still though, Tanks are used often in an ADC meta, so it is fine.

